Transcription.Text: But he has never signed the cheque. The jolt had to come; and unfortunately it does not seem to have come as cheaply as at first appeared. Dr. O'Brien may have taken one of the the tides in the affairs of men; omitted, Katanga might have straggled on to a worse tragedy.
